@startuml

[*] --> CreatedAccount : create account
CreatedAccount --> LoggedIn : login
LoggedIn --> AppliedForVisa : apply for visa, make payment, accept application
AppliedForVisa --> ViewedStatus : view status
ViewedStatus --> CheckedStatus : check status
CheckedStatus --> CanceledApplication : cancel application
CanceledApplication --> ModifiedDetails : modify details
ModifiedDetails --> ViewedDetails : view details
ViewedDetails --> ViewedPurpose : view purpose, update status based on document check
ViewedPurpose --> ProvidedFeedback : provide feedback
ProvidedFeedback --> LoggedOut : log out

@enduml
